restaurant_info.name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Chicken Badami Shorba
menu_items.description: Light bodied chicken soup with a hint of freshly chopped mint leaves finished with diced chicken and almond flakes.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Mutton Paya Shorba
menu_items.description: Robust, rejuvenating, overnight simmered goat trotter and millet broth with black pepper and fresh coriander.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Tamatar Dhaniya Shorba
menu_items.description: Zesty vine ripe tomatoes and fresh coriander soup, mildly spiced and served with carom crisps.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Dahi Kebab
menu_items.description: Velvety, cardamom and fresh coriander infused, hung youghurt kabab, deep fried.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Hara Bhara Kebab
menu_items.description: Delicate, hung curd and cashew filled spinach patty, shallow fried.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Tandoori Mushroom
menu_items.description: Button mushrooms marinated in fresh herbs and in-house tandoori masala, char-grilled in Tandoor
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Tandoori Malai Broccoli
menu_items.description: "Cream - malai", cashew butter and cardamom marinated broccoli, char-grilled in tandoor.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Bharwan Paneer Tikka
menu_items.description: Cheddar cheese and bell pepper "stuffed - bharwan" fresh cottage cheese "chunks - tikka", marinated and char-grilled in tandoor.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Chicken Malai Tikka
menu_items.description: Melt in the mouth, tandoor cooked chicken tikka, marinated with "cream - malai", cashew butter and cardamom.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Chicken Trio
menu_items.description: An impeccable potpourri of tikkas - the classic Chicken Tikka, the delicate Malai Tikka and The Bhatti Kabab.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Chicken Tikka
menu_items.description: Boneless morsels of chicken "tikka", marinated overnight in yoghurt and our secret spice blend, chargrilled in tandoor.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: The Original Tandoori Chicken
menu_items.description: Yoghurt and secret spice marinated, succulent, on the bone, tandoor roasted chicken. Created by Mokha Singh in the 1920's at Peshawar.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: The Original Chicken Pakora
menu_items.description: A scrumptious creation of Kundan Lal Jaggi at Daryaganj in 1947, crisp batter fried chicken scented with hand pounded carom and coriander seeds. We serve a boneless version of this classic.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Chicken Seekh Kebab
menu_items.description: Lean Chicken morsels grounded with fresh herbs and char-grilled in Tandoor
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Bhatti Chicken
menu_items.description: Chicken thighs, steeped in a distinctive spicy yoghurt and mustard oil marinade, char-grilled in Tandoor
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Mutton Seekh Kebab
menu_items.description: Zestful and rugged fresh green chilli and secret spice infused, mutton mince kebab of the finest quality, popularised by Kundan Lal Jaggi at Daryaganj in 1947.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Amritsari Mutton Chop
menu_items.description: A delicacy from Amritsar, premium grade mutton mince patty spiked with hand pounded coriander seeds, dry chilli and garam masala, pan-fried and embellished with toasted garlic flakes.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Sole Fish Tikka
menu_items.description: Boneless "chunks - tikka" of River Sole fish, marinated with lemon juice, mustard and carom seeds, gently cooked on coal embers.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Amritsari Fish Pakora
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Charrey Aloo
menu_items.description: A sumptuous dish that is made in every home, our rendition is, "bullet - charrey" or baby potatoes with mustard, cumin and fennel.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Kadhai Mushroom
menu_items.description: Prepared in the "Indian wok - kadhai", fresh mushrooms stir-fried with bell pepper juliennes, tomatoes, spring onion, crushed toasted coriander seeds and tomato gravy.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Malai Kofta
menu_items.description: A celebratory dish, cashew and vegetable stuffed cottage cheese dumplings in a titillating saffron-cream gravy.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Channa Masala
menu_items.description: A staple from Punjab, chickpeas gently simmered with whole spices and then finished with our secret spice.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Saag Paneer
menu_items.description: Pan-fried cottage cheese with creamy "spinach puree - saag", garlic and whole spices, tempered with coriander seeds and red chilli.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: The Original Butter Paneer
menu_items.description: House special, tandoor cooked paneer tikka in a delectable gravy made with hand crushed vine ripe tomatoes and a bit of butter, the dish is invigorated with a fresh tempering of green chillies and ginger juliennes.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: The Original 1947 Dal Makhani
menu_items.description: This original recipe by Kundan Lal Jaggi is prepared with overnight simmered black lentils, bit of butter, dry fenugreek leaves and freshly pureed vine ripe tomatoes.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Yellow Dal Double Tadka
menu_items.description: Perfect cooked trio of lentils, "tempered twice - double tadka" first with cumin and later finished with dry red chilli and ghee.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Paneer Lababdar
menu_items.description: Lababdar style is amongst the most robust, "cottage cheese - paneer" cooked with onion and capsicum in a thick-creamy-tomato gravy.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Baingan Ka Bharta
menu_items.description: An all time favourite recipe of smokey, charcoal roasted aubergine hash with onions, tomatoes, ginger, fresh coriander and red chilli.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Mixed Vegetables
menu_items.description: An exquisit "melange - miloni" of the seasons prime "vegetables - subz" cooked in a zesty, mildly spiced sauce.
menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Butter Paneer Masala
menu_items.description: Our modern day version is prepared with a buttery, creamy, velvety, fine tomato sauce and tandoor cooked paneer tikka.

menu_items.name: Aloo Gobhi

menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: The Original Egg Makhani

menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani

menu_items.name: Egg Curry

menu_items.restaurant_name: Daryaganj - By The Inventors Of Butter Chicken And Dal Makhani
